page-description: Portfolio with some projects developed during my career as a software developer.

project-description.fretec: The Fretec Entregas is an application for independent couriers who want to carry out freight in the city of Natal/RN. The app gives the delivery person a previously calculated smart route.
project-description.resolve-tudo: App to find any type of service provider quickly and easily.
project-description.cardiometrics: Cardiologists with different specialties who aim to form a medical opinion team, with multidisciplinary integration as a way of promoting knowledge and assistance in cardiology.
project-description.confia-shop: Confia.shop is a platform for selling products through a digital menu. The idea is that customers can choose and pay for your products without the need for a salesperson nearby.
project-description.lcc: LCC is a financial solutions marketplace, where you fill your credit needs, and LCC does analysis research with several banks at the same time, to find the best proposal that meets your conditions.
project-description.engegrout: Engineering platform aimed at organizing and conducting inspections, audits, assessments, expert opinions, and evaluations entirely remotely.
